requirement.text:
For each step if step order is different from:
0x00: PWM order ; 
0x01: Current order ; 
0x02: Velocity Control order type; 
0x03: Velocity Control + backup PWM order type;
0x04: Voltage order type;
0x05: Velocity Control + backup Current order type; 
0x06: Velocity Control + backup Voltage order
Then step is invalid.
